Mercy Hatton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mercy_Hatton 0 Mercy Hatton (25 January 1891 – 26 January 1986) was a British actress. She was born in Bromley, Kent, England as Constance Mercy Bird.Hatton was married to Wilfred (Russell) Mallinson. She died in 1986 in Bray, County Wicklow, Republic of Ireland.
